---------------------------------------------------------------------

The file you must edit is jeremy.jpg - you can open it in any TEXT editor.

The random quotes are located in stuf.txt.

You must also copy over a font file of your choosing to the same directory in which jeremy.jpg is located.
The Verdana font (verdana.ttf) works best.

Cheers,

Michael Soares (mikesoares.com)